title: Trailer: Ladies First with Laura Brown
description:
InStyle editor-in-chief Laura Brown talks to legendary ladies about how they do it—and what we can learn from them. Joining us this season: Michelle Pfeiffer, LaLa Anthony, Niecy Nash, Congresswoman Katie Porter, and many more.
